<emphasis box="[727,891,1922,1943]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="357">Lixus canescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: A—habitat with the flowering 
<taxonomicName box="[1216,1380,1921,1943]" class="Demospongiae" family="Crambeidae" genus="Crambe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poecilosclerida" pageId="7" pageNumber="357" phylum="Porifera" rank="species" species="pontica">
